# Group User

API resources used by individual users.

## Account [/account]

Resource for working with user account information.

### Get Account Information [GET]

Action for retrieving a user's account information.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "email": "user@test.io"
        }

### Update Account Information [PUT]

Action for updating a user's account information.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "id": 1,
                "email": "user@example.com"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "id": 1,
                "email": "user@example.com"
            }
